      "comment": "RICOCHET RIPPLE (1) goes very well this course and distance starting 15 times for five wins and five minors. Recorded a 2 length win (20.25) in a Grade 3/4 last time at Capalaba. Expected to be in the finish. DUFFMAN (3) was strongly fancied and drifted back but wound up hard to hit the frame, 1.75 lengths from the winner (20.31) at Capalaba in Mix 5. Bold showing expected. INTO OBLIVION (2) was below best at his last couple, the latest finishing sixth at this track, but was among the placings at Q Straight three back. Well placed here and should do much better. SEAWAY CRUISER (8) is chasing another win after a quick 21.76 win latest. Don't underestimate.",
